This is a placeholder for the PNG icon. You'll need to convert the SVG to PNG format.

To create the PNG icon from the SVG:
1. Open pwa-icon.svg in a graphics editor (like GIMP, Photoshop, or online tool like CloudConvert)
2. Export as PNG at 192x192 pixels
3. Save as pwa-192x192.png in the public folder

Alternatively, you can use an online converter:
- Go to https://cloudconvert.com/svg-to-png
- Upload pwa-icon.svg
- Set dimensions to 192x192
- Download and replace this file
